      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) used under a documented QMS with version control, regression testing, and change control records on file.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is deployed under the sponsor's ISO 13485-compliant QMS. Software validation records, regression test suite results, and version-locked configuration files were reviewed and found complete. Achieved level equals required level; factor satisfied."
