      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the pedicle screw shank and rod junction. QoI (von Mises stress at critical cross-section) changed 0.6% from medium to fine mesh. GCI = 1.4%. Discretization error is adequately controlled; required level achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual convergence to 1e-5 or better for all load steps; energy balance error <0.1%.",
